              <header id="masthead"><nav></nav></header>      
                            <div id="site-wrapper" role="main">
          <div id="default-content">
        
          <p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p>
  
    <article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6527372">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Dungeons &amp; Dragons fans have a new, multiverse-spanning adventure to read. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dungeons-Dragons-Worlds-Realms-Adventures/dp/0593835506?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Worlds &amp; Realms: Adventures from Greyhawk to Faerun and Beyond book</a> released today, October 29. The hardcover volume was written to celebrate the classic tabletop roleplaying game's 50th anniversary and will read like a narrative-driven art book, taking readers on an illustrated tour of the many realms in the D&amp;D franchise through the eyes of various adventuring parties. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dungeons-Dragons-Worlds-Realms-Adventures/dp/0593835506?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Amazon is offering a nice launch discount</a> that drops the price of the new D&amp;D book to $35 (list price is $50).</p><div title="6527372 - D&amp;D Worlds &amp; Realms: Adventures from Greyhawk to Faerun and Beyond preorder" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="2770" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6527372 - D&amp;D Worlds &amp; Realms: Adventures from Greyhawk to Faerun and Beyond preorder" data-collection="">             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dungeons-Dragons-Worlds-Realms-Adventures/dp/0593835506?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Dungeons-Dragons-Worlds-Realms-Adventures\/dp\/0593835506?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Dungeons-Dragons-Worlds-Realms-Adventures/dp/0593835506?tag=gamespot-promos-20">Dungeons &amp; Dragons - Worlds &amp; Realms: Adventures from Greyhawk to Faerun and Beyond</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dungeons-Dragons-Worlds-Realms-Adventures/dp/0593835506?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Dungeons-Dragons-Worlds-Realms-Adventures\/dp\/0593835506?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Dungeons-Dragons-Worlds-Realms-Adventures/dp/0593835506?tag=gamespot-promos-20">$35 (was $50)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p dir="ltr">According to the book's description, Worlds &amp; Realms: Adventures from Greyhawk to Faerun and Beyond features many of the lands seen in all five editions of Dungeons &amp; Dragons and its expansions across its 368 pages. Each chapter offers history and lore tidbits about the featured realm--however, instead of reading like a traditional D&amp;D sourcebook, these insights are delivered by the mage Mordenkainen, giving readers an in-universe "mage’s-eye view of [each realm's] unique features, creatures, and characters."</p><p dir="ltr">Along with the mage's musings, you'll find short stories set in these various realms written by award-winning D&amp;D writers like Jaleigh Johnson, Jody Houser, Eric Campbell, Jasmine Bhullar, and Geoffrey Golden. The book's lore dumps and short stories are accompanied by artwork from every edition of D&amp;D, including all-new original illustrations that open each chapter.</p></div>                      </div><hr><p dir="ltr">If you're a D&amp;D fan, chances are you're also into Baldur's Gate 3, which is set in the Sword Coast region of the D&amp;D realm Faerun. Soon, you'll be able to add the characters from the acclaimed CRPG into your tabletop sessions with the <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/baldurs-gate-3-best-characters-are-now-dungeons-dragons-miniatures/1100-6526851/" data-ref-id="1100-6526851">official D&amp;D minis of Baldur's Gate 3 party members and enemies</a>. The minis launch early next year and are available to preorder now.</p><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4389925-4385792-4377545-bg3-tabletop%281%29.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4389925" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4389925-4385792-4377545-bg3-tabletop%281%29.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4389925"></a><figcaption>Dungeons &amp; Dragons Icons of the Realm - Baldur's Gate 3 Character Minis Box Set</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4389925-4385792-4377545-bg3-tabletop%281%29.jpg"></figure><h2 dir="ltr">Dungeons &amp; Dragons Icons of the Realm: Baldur's Gate Figures</h2><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://shop.wizkids.com/collections/pre-order-collection/products/d-d-icons-of-the-realms-baldurs-gate-3-character-boxed-set" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Baldur's Gate 3 Character Minis Box Set</a> -- $50 | Releases Q1 2025</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://shop.wizkids.com/collections/pre-order-collection/products/d-d-icons-of-the-realms-adventures-from-baldurs-gate-8-ct-booster-brick" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Adventures in Baldur's Gate Monster Booster Bundle</a> -- $200 | Releases Q1 2025</li></ul><hr><p dir="ltr">Similarly, the first wave of <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/baldurs-gate-3-funko-pop-collectible-preorder-astarion-shadowheart-karlach/1100-6527207/" data-ref-id="1100-6527207">Funko Pop! Baldur's Gate 3 figures</a> featuring Astarion, Shadowheart, and Karlach are dropping this winter. All three vinyl figures recently went up for preorder at Amazon, Entertainment Earth, and GameStop, but they're already selling out.</p><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4389924-4385801-bg3pophero.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4389924" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4389924-4385801-bg3pophero.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4389924"></a><figcaption>Funko Pop! Karlach, Astarion, and Shadowheart vynil figures</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4389924-4385801-bg3pophero.jpg"></figure><h2 dir="ltr">Baldur's Gate 3 Funko Pop Vinyl Figures</h2><p><strong>Amazon</strong></p><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Funko-Pop-Collectible-Toy-Figure/dp/B0D19DV4YB?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Astarion with Dagger</a> -- (Sold out) | Releases December 16</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Funko-Pop-Collectible-Toy-Figure/dp/B0D1979PLB?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Shadowheart with Artifact</a> -- $13 | Releases December 16</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Funko-Pop-Collectible-Toy-Figure/dp/B0D19R5Y5S?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Karlach 